::Hot Rod::

He comes out of the CR.
&quot;I&#39;m going to look for some of our guys. Make sure they are ok.&quot;
He makes his way to the cargo hold, Hot Rod knew that the old Dinobot leader was on the ship.
&quot;Grimlock, you in here? You ok?&quot;

::????::

Meanwhile in the mess hall, we see broken tables and bars. Different Cybertronian drinks, are smashed everywhere.

&quot;I knew I should have never went to that outpost. Now I get stuck on this ship, and we crash on god knows where.&quot;

The ruble is pushed aside, as the aged and wise Autobot Kup emerges.

&quot;They had to choose me. I know the outpost was watching the transwarp wormhole, and that it was important. So I understand the Autobot command wanting an Autobot stationed with the Maximals there, but did it have to really be me? Man, I really should have refused this assignment. If it wasn&#39;t for me trying to keep an eye on Hot Rod, i probably would have...&quot;

Kup realizes that he has been babaling on to himself, and stops.

He walks out, and down the halls. He arrives in the CR room, where he sees Talos.
&quot;Autobot, Kup, reporting. What happaned?&quot;

